GET http://localhost:3001/api/users/65f3a8e1b164b6e5c2c65123

### Update user (replace ID with a valid user ID)
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/users/65f3a8e1b164b6e5c2c65123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "updateduser",
  "email": "updated@example.com"
}

